WEBVTT

00:01.410 --> 00:05.562
<i> (dramatic music)</i>

00:05.655 --> 00:07.748
(coughing)

00:07.842 --> 00:09.324
(sighs)

00:09.493 --> 00:10.992
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

00:11.161 --> 00:13.661
(glass shattering,
flames bursting)

00:13.830 --> 00:20.602
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

00:24.341 --> 00:26.083
Rot in hell.

00:26.252 --> 00:29.528
<i> SINGER:</i>
<i> ♪ Bring me a higher love ♪</i>

00:30.865 --> 00:35.701
<i> ♪ Bring me a higher love,</i>
<i> oh, Lord ♪</i>

00:35.928 --> 00:38.945
Lord, direct my footsteps
according to your word

00:39.114 --> 00:41.206
and let no sin rule over me.

00:41.375 --> 00:43.784
Thank you for protecting
my family.

00:43.952 --> 00:46.879
You've kept us free
from tragedy and illness

00:47.048 --> 00:49.606
and you have given us abundance
of wealth.

00:49.775 --> 00:50.716
Everything.

00:50.943 --> 00:52.867
As long as I have breath
in my body

00:53.036 --> 00:54.369
and your spirit in my heart.

00:54.463 --> 00:58.057
I am your servant
and your faithful soldier.

00:59.285 --> 01:00.450
Amen!

01:00.619 --> 01:02.043
-(chuckles)
-Oh!

01:02.212 --> 01:04.396
Now, let's just see.
Oh, yeah.

01:04.565 --> 01:05.956
-Oh!
-Look in my eyes.

01:06.049 --> 01:07.882
Let me see you.

01:08.051 --> 01:10.569
<i> SINGER:</i>
<i> ♪ Where's that higher love ♪</i>

01:10.738 --> 01:14.907
Well, every superhero
needs a cape, Mama.

01:15.076 --> 01:17.984
Oh, Rose, you hush up.
You hear your daughter?

01:18.079 --> 01:21.246
<i> ♪ Think about it</i>
<i> there must be higher love ♪</i>

01:21.473 --> 01:25.918
<i>♪ Down in the heart</i>
<i>or hidden in the stars above ♪</i>

01:26.087 --> 01:29.088
