Take camera one.

01:29.256 --> 01:30.905
All right.

01:31.074 --> 01:32.649
Y'all are listening today.

01:32.818 --> 01:35.836
Hold steady, camera one.
Hold steady.

01:35.930 --> 01:39.765
Can you hear me in Hong Kong?
From Norway to LA?

01:39.934 --> 01:43.751
Can you hear me in Australia?
The San Francisco Bay.

01:43.846 --> 01:46.847
The Lord is calling on you now.
He's waiting on the line.

01:46.941 --> 01:47.831
Are you ready?

01:48.000 --> 01:49.090
(cheers and applause)

01:49.259 --> 01:51.685
Are you ready?
Are you ready?

01:51.779 --> 01:52.945
