will be on the teleprompter.

01:55.616 --> 01:58.508
-Okay.
-Eric, stick to the line.

01:58.677 --> 01:59.934
(cheers and applause)

02:00.103 --> 02:01.194
Go get 'em, baby.

02:01.363 --> 02:02.679
(whispering)
I'll see you out there.

02:02.848 --> 02:04.790
-Eric, honey?
-EUGENE: Come on, son.

02:04.959 --> 02:07.868
<i> THOMAS: ♪ Try to see</i>
<i> falling behind ♪</i>

02:08.036 --> 02:09.686
Look how far we've come.

02:09.855 --> 02:13.357
25 years.
All things are possible in Him.

02:13.525 --> 02:15.450
-In you.
-In us.

02:15.619 --> 02:17.118
Oh, Lord.

02:17.287 --> 02:20.622
Oh, it's nice of the Reverend
to try and upstage me

02:20.790 --> 02:22.866
on my own network
on today of all days.

02:23.035 --> 02:25.869
He'd be nothing without you.

02:26.038 --> 02:29.631
Rose, I think we should get
the wings.

02:29.799 --> 02:31.208
<i> THOMAS: Be that higher love,</i>

02:31.377 --> 02:34.636
and stick around for an extra
special 25th anniversary.

02:34.804 --> 02:36.488
Yeah, that's right!

02:36.657 --> 02:37.990
Go on.
Show Margaret your love.

02:38.159 --> 02:39.900
<i> And may God bless you now.</i>

02:40.068 --> 02:42.736
NORAH: And go.

02:42.905 --> 02:47.240
Live from Sunshine Studios
in beautiful New Orleans.

02:47.409 --> 02:52.487
<i> Ladies and gentlemen,</i>
<i> Margaret Monreaux!</i>

02:52.656 --> 02:56.175
(cheering)

02:56.343 --> 02:58.844
Wow!
Hello!

02:59.013 --> 03:00.737
(upbeat music playing)

03:00.906 --> 03:01.922
<i> SINGER: ♪ On the wings ♪</i>

03:02.090 --> 03:03.498
