03:03.667 --> 03:05.350
Unbelievable.

03:05.519 --> 03:06.760
Hello!

03:06.929 --> 03:08.854
(cheers and applause)

03:09.023 --> 03:11.415
Oh, stop that!
No!

03:11.583 --> 03:13.358
(cheers and applause)

03:13.527 --> 03:16.269
I did that!
Look what they made me do!

03:16.438 --> 03:18.438
(cheering continues)

03:18.607 --> 03:19.847
Love you!

03:20.016 --> 03:22.275
Thank you for those warm,
welcoming words.

03:23.429 --> 03:26.096
There is something that I need
to say to all of you.

03:26.265 --> 03:29.616
You and the Lord give me
the strength to do what I do,

03:29.785 --> 03:30.709
so thank you.

03:30.878 --> 03:32.269
(cheers and applause)

03:32.396 --> 03:36.048
Now this mama bear has been
starving herself for a month

03:36.217 --> 03:39.125
