on my carpet.

03:52.474 --> 03:55.025
<i> MAN: Bite that apple, baby.</i>
<i> Yeah, bite it good.</i>

03:56.237 --> 03:59.129
Sorry, Kansas City Beef.
Your card was declined.

03:59.298 --> 04:01.240
<i> What? Can you--can</i>
<i> you run it again?</i>

04:01.408 --> 04:02.632
-Ginger.
-Yeah.

04:02.801 --> 04:03.650
You better go check
on your mom.

04:03.744 --> 04:05.302
She's watching
that TV show again.

04:05.471 --> 04:06.161
(groans)

04:07.990 --> 04:10.398
(rooster crowing)

04:10.567 --> 04:11.917
<i> MARGARET: Thank you</i>
<i> to all my mama bears</i>

04:12.144 --> 04:14.811
<i> for 25 years of support.</i>

04:14.980 --> 04:16.922
