I give you Sunny Club.

05:35.577 --> 05:38.411
(cheers and applause)

05:38.580 --> 05:39.671
<i> (upbeat music)</i>

05:39.840 --> 05:41.673
(chanting)
Sunny Club, Sunny Club.

05:41.842 --> 05:43.583
