the planned speech.

06:09.778 --> 06:10.927
-No.
-But I--

06:11.020 --> 06:12.779
Subtlety is the footbridge
to integrity.

06:12.873 --> 06:14.039
Amen.

06:14.266 --> 06:16.357
True integrity means
you're the same in public

06:16.526 --> 06:17.617
as you are in private.

06:17.786 --> 06:19.786
