-You attract bees with honey,

06:19.880 --> 06:21.438
not Butt Butter.

06:21.607 --> 06:23.123
Walk with me, Eric.

06:23.291 --> 06:26.200
♪ ♪

06:26.369 --> 06:29.279
I rue the day that Eric
married that man's sister.

06:29.448 --> 06:31.448
They are family now.
We have to treat him as such.

06:31.617 --> 06:33.633
